  "texts": [
    "In summary, the rule-based approach provides a baseline for the ACOSQE task but may have limitations.",
    "This paper will offer a comprehensive overview of the rule-based approach, considering it from both the pros and cons perspectives.",
    "• Pros -Rule-based approach in ACOSQE provides explicit control over the extraction process, allowing researchers to define specific rules and patterns for identifying aspects, opinions, and sentiment polarity.",
    "-Rule-based approach can be effective in scenarios where the domain-specific knowledge is well-defined and can be easily translated into extraction rules.",
    "-Rule-based approach can be computationally efficient and require less training data than machine learning-based approaches."
